Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,With high hopes, humans\Nleave Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...to begin a new life in\Nthe space colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But the United Earth Sphere\NAlliance gains military power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.35,0:01:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...and in the name of\NJustice and Peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.39,0:01:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...seizes control of one\Ncolony after the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is After Colony 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.26,0:01:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To counter the Alliance's\Ntyranny, rebel colonists...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.40,0:01:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...bring new arsenals\Nto the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...disguising them as\Nshooting stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:02:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Alliance headquarters\Ncatches on to this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to leave the room\Nnow, Vice Foreign Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time you\Npeople realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...that you're posing the\Ngreatest threat of all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! We've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.87,0:02:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right over here so\Nhurry and come kill me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Foreign Minister Darlian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope this'll be a very\Nsuccessful trip for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with a little\Nsocializing is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to discuss\Nwith a Specials officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty harsh words, Minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here on orders\Nfrom my superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't take out your\Nfrustrations on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Never forget how beautiful\Nthe Earth looks from afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never see it again,\NDarlian.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you sighing about;\Nsomething bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The colonies are amidst\Na beautiful sea of stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So why is it they don't\Nseem to sparkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't agree with you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena's in the colonies\Nthis very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be sparkling\Nmuch brighter than usual!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Target: North Pacific Ocean,\NOZ supply base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Darlian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So rumors of Earth's chronic\Nfinancial crisis are false.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you couldn't afford to\Ntake a shuttle for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish that were\Nthe only rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The latest false rumors\Nthroughout the Alliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.43,0:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...are much more grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumors that we're planning\Nan attack against Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good could result\Nfrom our attacking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The purpose of this visit\Nis to find out for ourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...whether or not those\Nrumors are accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hope there's no\Ntruth to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Earthlings think the\Npeaceful, courteous colonists...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...would want to start a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Miss Une.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have diplomatic\Nauthorization from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't allow you\Nto sit in on this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd like to know the\Noutcome of the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course.\N- Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when it all ends;\Nor rather when it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.49,0:06:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Relena.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going out shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you an escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's much safer here\Nthan it is on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She must've forgotten this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,These accusations are unjust!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We've never heard of this\NProject Meteor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...or the new type\Nof mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.66,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Darlian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does the Alliance find\Nit difficult to believe us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten more seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here; I think you forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.49,0:07:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Go after the girl and kill her\Nif she tries to resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Father?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Mr. Darlian okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No other survivors!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just take Mr. Darlian!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's taken Darlian's\Ndaughter and is escaping!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Block the exits!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise you'll get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.27,0:08:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing\Nwith my father?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do as we say\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.46,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This injection should\Nhelp you relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get Father to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else he'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The hospital's too risky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're probably already\Nguarding the hospitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We have good doctors\Nin our organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie still!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your biological\Nfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your real name is\NRelena Peacecraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the daughter of\Nthe Peacecraft family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...who once advocated\NComplete Pacifism.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a senator who served\Ntheir country in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But long ago the kingdom was\Ndemolished by the Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I took you in as my\Ndaughter when I escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the\NOZ organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,NOOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The medication's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The mobile suit's repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks pal; I owe you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.10,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem, as long as\NI get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an excellent client.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We made it just in time\Nfor my next mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least tell me\Nwhat your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Quatre\NRaberba Winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.97,0:11:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you must call me\Nsomething, then Trowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Trowa Barton.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.54,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Trowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Quatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we let him go like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows the location\Nof this base...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not the talkative type.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He could attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost wish he would.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at least I'd be\Nable to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What a drag; boring guard\Nduty for two whole hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, is something wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to get to the target\Npoint for my mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The staff here is skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure it gets completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this 20 year-old\Nsuit is gonna be useful to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably more advanced\Nthan any OZ mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's currently available.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This Tallgeese suit is the\Nprototype for all mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Even those Gundams were built\Nbased on this Tallgeese design.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry for\Nyour loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If only we'd become aware\Nof the situation earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.18,0:13:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...we could've avoided\Nthis tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Une, any comments on{\i0}\N{\i1}this terrible accident?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm saddened by what has{\i0}\N{\i1}happened here today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no idea there were such{\i0}\N{\i1}evil terrorists in this colony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're told that Vice Foreign{\i0}\N{\i1}Minister Darlian...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...and his daughter{\i0}\N{\i1}were kidnapped.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're investigating the{\i0}\N{\i1}situation ourselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're unaware of the{\i0}\N{\i1}terrorists' true objectives...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but if this reflects the{\i0}\N{\i1}feelings of the whole colony...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...we'll be forced to take{\i0}\N{\i1}military action.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.65,0:14:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W- Wait a minute, Lieutenant{\i0}\N{\i1}Colonel Une!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Excuse me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm conducting a terrorist{\i0}\N{\i1}investigation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's made us out to be\Na bunch of terrorists!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just what you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,My father died because you\Ndidn't take him to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.63,0:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry for\Nwhat happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get revenge for his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ did it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ killed my father, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll just end up\Ngetting killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.79,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if I do get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll kill you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do you wanna{\i0}\N{\i1}shoot him?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No need to apologize Father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm old enough to understand{\i0}\N{\i1}how important your business is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero...I want to\Nsee you, Heero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean\NHeero Yuy, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.33,0:15:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That was some performance\Nby Lady Une.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Mr. Darlian?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Relena...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Still worried aren't you, Zechs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hiding too many secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're detecting an\Nenormous heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and two guard Leos\Nhave disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare all mobile suits\Nfor combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Visibility is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't confirm anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please feel free to call me\NDr. J, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not,\NI'm a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. J.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one that sent\NHeero to Earth, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But who in their right mind\Nwould've thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.26,0:17:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...he'd end up in the same\Nschool as Darlian's daughter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that rascal doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying\Nto get him to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That young lad is an\Nagent of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.90,0:17:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Heero was young,\Nwe've taught him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...a wide range of combat\Nstrategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought him up as\Na professional assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For the peace of the colonies,\Nof course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing can't possibly\Nlead us to peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It leads directly to peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wars are started by people\Nand they end with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero's ordered to attack\Nthe dangerous, evil people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...responsible for\Nstarting wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But there must be more\Npeaceful solutions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Twenty years ago, we\Nbelieved that ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought mankind\Ncouldn't be so foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That no one could possibly\Nwish for a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The colonies were started\Nby scientists like myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.33,0:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...and by laborers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Our ancestors did everything\Nthey could to form the colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After over 100 years\Nof hard work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...we enjoyed a normal\Nlifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.54,0:18:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And exactly twenty years ago,\Nwe were living peacefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...under the ruler of\Nall colonies, Heero Yuy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero Yuy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,His name still lives on\Ntoday as a legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...among the residents\Nof our colonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where we came up\Nwith the lad's code name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His code name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Peaceful times in the colonies\Ndidn't last for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've felt a leader\Npromoting peace was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero Yuy was assassinated\Nby some organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From then on, communication\Nceased between the colonies...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it became an excuse to\Nfortify the Alliance Military.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ was responsible\Nfor the assassination...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...and wanted to wage\Na war in the Earth Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know OZ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last thing\Nmy father said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To watch out for OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So who are you making\NHeero fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All of OZ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.70,0:19:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We must stop their ambitions...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...to take over the United\NAlliance Military...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and dictate the Earth Sphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, why does Heero have\Nto take on that enormous task?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should he be responsible\Nfor doing all that by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He understands the emotional\Npains that the colony residents...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...have endured over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Still!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we're after\Nthe same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, aren't you gonna{\i0}\N{\i1}at least respond?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Locked on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.26,0:20:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like the two of us will\Nhave to fight it out after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be able to return\Nyou safely to Earth from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you help me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because of my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm his daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you had the same\Nlook in your eyes as Heero did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That genuine expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heero's actually a kind-hearted\Nyoung boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.53,0:21:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But Heero's very dedicated\Nto his mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from him\Nif you value your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've returned the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.08,0:22:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always be your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thrown into a new,\Nuncertain destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...Relena returns to the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What awaits her is\Na school party...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.07,0:23:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...and notice of Heero's\Ntransfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing Heero's secret,\NRelena figures out...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.54,0:23:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...that the transfer is related\Nto his next mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.91,0:23:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,OZ assassins come for Relena,\Nand Heero ends up saving her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, on Gundam Wing, Episode 6,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"Party Night".
